WEBVTT

00:05.325 --> 00:06.524
Please?

00:07.845 --> 00:09.045
Don't hurt me any more.

00:12.093 --> 00:14.368
(sobbing)
Please, just kill me.

00:14.912 --> 00:16.111
Not yet, Becky.

00:17.014 --> 00:18.414
We're still having fun.

00:18.415 --> 00:19.515
No.

00:19.516 --> 00:21.718
(gasping)
No. No.

00:22.553 --> 00:24.754
(gasping)

00:26.000 --> 00:32.073
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:34.164 --> 00:37.033
(breathing heavily)

00:45.776 --> 00:47.210
How did the judge rule?

00:47.211 --> 00:49.412
Unfortunately,
to void this felony conviction

00:49.413 --> 00:50.747
because the case was

00:50.748 --> 00:53.349
predicated solely
on tainted DNA evidence.

00:53.350 --> 00:54.984
Three out of five.

00:54.985 --> 00:56.653
So far,
that's the batting average

00:56.654 --> 00:58.187
of the DAs in other boroughs.

00:58.188 --> 01:00.957
Still, two criminals
back on the streets

01:00.958 --> 01:03.693
because of a lab tech's
shoddy work?

01:03.694 --> 01:05.028
(sighs)

01:05.029 --> 01:06.863
Thank you, Counselor.

01:06.864 --> 01:08.331
Thank you, Commissioner.

01:17.341 --> 01:18.474
Who's up next?

01:18.475 --> 01:20.343
Manhattan District Attorney,
sir.

01:20.344 --> 01:21.978
Send him in.

01:24.081 --> 01:26.282
Commissioner.

01:29.603 --> 01:32.088
Counselor.

01:32.089 --> 01:33.523
Please.

01:36.276 --> 01:39.262
So, where are we, Counselor?

01:39.263 --> 01:42.165
I've found grounds
to hold without bail and retry

01:42.166 --> 01:43.833
four of the
prisoners in question.

01:43.834 --> 01:45.201
Good.

01:45.202 --> 01:46.803
There are two
outstanding problems.

01:46.804 --> 01:49.105
Garth Kraver, pedophile.

01:49.106 --> 01:51.674
Convicted on three counts
of sexual conduct

01:51.675 --> 01:53.576
on a child
in the first degree.

01:53.577 --> 01:55.111
The judge is set to rule

01:55.112 --> 01:56.479
on whether to vacate
this conviction.

01:56.480 --> 01:58.681
Where do you think
the judge will come down?

01:58.682 --> 02:02.518
I'm worried, but not as worried
as I am about Dick Reed.

02:02.519 --> 02:04.687
(sighs)

02:04.688 --> 02:06.756
I've prosecuted
some animals before, but

02:06.757 --> 02:10.560
what he did to those three women
before he killed them...

02:11.729 --> 02:13.496
The worst of the worst.

02:13.497 --> 02:15.298
Our best chance on this is

02:15.299 --> 02:18.034
if I can get Becky Watalski
to testify

02:18.035 --> 02:19.802
in a new trial.

02:19.803 --> 02:21.537
I've gone to see her three times

02:21.538 --> 02:24.040
to persuade her
to testify, but...

02:25.109 --> 02:27.193
Becky is Reed's only
surviving victim.

02:27.194 --> 02:28.945
"Tortured for 19 hours.
She had

02:28.946 --> 02:32.148
"the presence of mind to free
herself from her burning bed

02:32.149 --> 02:34.617
by holding her bindings
over the flames."

02:34.618 --> 02:36.953
She was still able to provide
a detailed description

02:36.954 --> 02:38.221
that led us to Reed.

02:38.222 --> 02:39.389
We had enough

02:39.390 --> 02:40.757
DNA evidence to convict him

02:40.758 --> 02:42.759
on the three murder charges,

02:42.760 --> 02:44.660
and due to her fragile state,

02:44.661 --> 02:46.696
we did not have to try her case.

02:46.697 --> 02:48.264
We'll have a constant watch
on Reed,

02:48.265 --> 02:50.800
and you'll find a way
to put him back behind bars,

02:50.801 --> 02:52.568
Counselor.
(phone beeps)

02:52.569 --> 02:54.270
Kings County
DA's here, sir.

02:54.271 --> 02:56.973
See to him, Baker.

03:04.531 --> 03:06.249
So, where's your boss?

03:06.250 --> 03:08.367
On a plane to Scottsdale.

03:08.368 --> 03:10.586
Nice of him
to drop this mess in your lap.

03:10.587 --> 03:12.155
In Charley's defense,

03:12.156 --> 03:14.574
he was scheduled to speak
at the DA's conference

03:14.575 --> 03:15.892
months ago.

03:15.893 --> 03:17.960
Charley Rossellini wasn't shy
about taking credit

03:17.961 --> 03:21.431
when he put these perps away,
but now that the heat's on...

03:26.103 --> 03:29.055
You know, that son of a
bitch Reed was smiling

03:29.056 --> 03:30.773
through the
whole trial?

03:30.774 --> 03:32.442
Stay after him, sweetheart.

03:32.443 --> 03:34.610
I will, Dad.

03:39.983 --> 03:42.118
DANNY:
<i>I don't get it.</i>

03:42.119 --> 03:43.236
I don't get it.

03:43.237 --> 03:45.321
I busted my hump
trying to lock that guy up.

03:45.322 --> 03:46.989
Now he's gonna
get out of jail free

03:46.990 --> 03:49.992
because some lab nerd's
all stressed out and overworked?

03:49.993 --> 03:52.111
Ah, in a warm
lab, no less.

03:52.112 --> 03:53.279
Mm, with warm coffee.

03:53.280 --> 03:55.865
Oh, warm coffee.
Look.

03:55.866 --> 03:57.366
JACKIE: Oh, here comes
the prison bus.

03:57.367 --> 03:59.202
DANNY:
The slimeball express.

03:59.203 --> 04:00.736
WOMAN: Get up close,
right up front.

04:00.737 --> 04:02.205
Right this way.

04:09.930 --> 04:12.014
WOMAN: There he is, there he is.
(WOMAN 2) Yay!

04:12.015 --> 04:13.950
There he is!

04:13.951 --> 04:16.052
JACKIE:
Look at this party.

04:16.053 --> 04:17.320
Oh, geez.

04:18.137 --> 04:19.922
MAN:
Reed!

04:19.923 --> 04:21.390
There he is.
(applause)

04:21.391 --> 04:23.092
(laughing)
DANNY: Dick Reed, the rapist.

04:23.093 --> 04:25.058
JACKIE:
Don't forget murderer.

04:25.059 --> 04:26.428
DANNY:
It's disgusting.

04:26.429 --> 04:27.729
MAN:
Look this way.

04:27.730 --> 04:29.909
So that's what pure evil
looks like up close.

04:29.910 --> 04:30.556
Yeah.

04:30.581 --> 04:32.632
Makes his bus mates
who did their time

04:32.633 --> 04:34.650
look like saints.
Yeah, how about

04:34.651 --> 04:37.937
the whack job
welcoming committee?

04:37.938 --> 04:39.355
This guy's got a fan club.

04:39.356 --> 04:40.923
It's amazing.
You got to be

04:40.924 --> 04:44.861
some kind of nut to obsess
over a scumbag like this.

04:44.862 --> 04:46.762
- Excuse me.
- Excuse us.

04:46.763 --> 04:48.264
Taxi!

04:48.265 --> 04:51.433
Hey, Dick,
what's the rush?

04:53.821 --> 04:56.873
Oh, yeah.

04:56.874 --> 04:58.841
So you're the cop

04:58.842 --> 05:01.294
who worked the
Katie Snow case,

05:01.295 --> 05:03.713
unfortunate victim number two.

05:03.714 --> 05:07.617
Very vivid description
you gave that jury. Ooh!

05:07.618 --> 05:08.918
Yeah, I'm good like that.

05:08.919 --> 05:10.586
How about
we give you a ride?

05:10.587 --> 05:13.256
I mean, we're gonna be
all over your ass anyway, so,

05:13.257 --> 05:14.790
we might as well
get reacquainted.

05:14.791 --> 05:15.925
(laughs)

05:15.926 --> 05:17.426
That's a two-way
street, friend.

05:17.427 --> 05:18.561
- Really?
- Yeah.

05:18.562 --> 05:19.962
So, if you want to
keep your badge,

05:19.963 --> 05:21.597
better stay off my ass.
Really?

05:21.598 --> 05:24.433
Harassment. Section 2-40-26

05:24.434 --> 05:26.269
of the penal code.
Penal code.

05:26.270 --> 05:27.687
Look it up.

05:27.688 --> 05:31.107
I bet you studied up
a lot about penal codes.

05:31.108 --> 05:32.992
That's good for a rapist.

05:32.993 --> 05:34.643
Enjoy your reprieve.

05:34.644 --> 05:36.145
It won't last long.

05:36.146 --> 05:37.480
It was good seeing you, though,

05:37.481 --> 05:38.647
and your girlfriend.

05:38.648 --> 05:39.815
Partner.

05:39.816 --> 05:42.001
I'll bet.

05:43.003 --> 05:45.288
- I need a shower.
- Yeah.

05:46.874 --> 05:49.759
Hey, you stay on top
of that son of a bitch

05:49.760 --> 05:51.794
and don't let him
out of your sight.

05:51.795 --> 05:53.329
- Right.
- Go ahead.

05:54.381 --> 05:56.265
(sighs)

05:58.001 --> 06:02.001
<font color=#00ff00>♪ Blue Bloods 1x09 ♪</font>
<font color=#00ffff>Re-Do</font>
